description.narrative: COVID-19 caused an educational crisis that had an impact on children&39;s engagement and participation in education. UNICEF promoted activities focused on innovative and quality education, with an emphasis on including;the most vulnerable children. UNICEF developed several strategies: i) implementing the project “La visión del Plan Ceibal para Reimaginar la Educación” [“Plan Ceibal&39;s Vision for Reimagining Education”]; ii) promoting the global strategy of "Reimagining Education" based on listening to adolescents; iii) gathering evidence and knowledge; iv) implementing a model of socioeducational intervention in vulnerable contexts; v) supporting teacher training; and vi) designing an inclusive digital book for schools. | Status:Partially met | As-of Date:21/12/2021
